  - m_Id: 4119208194093056
    m_Localized: BACK
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4824198197948416
    m_Localized: Spend your coins to build more towers!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4824198227308544
    m_Localized: "Pay attention to each tower\u2019s attack range."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4824198227308545
    m_Localized: Place towers beside enemy paths for better results!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4824198227308546
    m_Localized: Sometimes upgrading towers is better than building new ones.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4824198227308547
    m_Localized: Different enemies require different types of towers.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4824198227308548
    m_Localized: Place high-damage towers where they can attack the longest.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4824198227308549
    m_Localized: Watch the enemy route before placing your towers.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4824198227308550
    m_Localized: "Don\u2019t let your coins sit idle. Turn them into firepower!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4826130945814528
    m_Localized: GAME OVER
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
